    "For DeepSeek-R1-Zero, we use rule-based rewards to deliver precise feedback for data in mathematical, coding and logical reasoning domains.",
    "For DeepSeek-R1, we extend this approach by incorporating both rule-based rewards for reasoning-oriented data and model-based rewards for general data, thereby enhancing the adaptability of the learning process across diverse domains.",
    "Rule-based rewards.",
    "Our rule-based reward system mainly consists of two types of reward: accuracy rewards and format rewards.",
    "Accuracy rewards evaluate whether the response is correct."
